,
N'aham--I; vaisvanarah--by My plenary portion as the digesting fire;bhutva--becoming; praninam--of all living entities; deham--body;asritah--situated; prana--outgoing air; apana--down-going air;samayuktah--keep balance; pacami--digest; annam--foodstuff; catuhvidham--four kinds of.'
